    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>Are you a ball committee member? Use the Add/Edit button</p>
            <p>Need to get in touch? Contact me at admin (at) mayball.info!</p>
            <p>Alternatively, make a pull request on <a href="https://github.com/Xemorr/MayBallInfo">github</a></p>
